✅ Final Summary (Without Lombok)

✔ No Lombok annotations used (manual getters, setters, constructors).
✔ Matches Swagger structure (error wrapper with error details inside).
✔ requestId is generated only in exceptions and returned in error responses.
✔ Covers validation errors (400), system errors (500), and business logic errors.

